title: Doyle Lawson and Quicksilver
description:
Smooth Christmas bluegrass from the 1991 edition of Quicksilver: 
Doyle Lawson, mandolin & vocals
Jim Mills, banjo & vocals
Shelton Feazell, electric bass, guitar & vocals
John R. Bowman, guitar, electric bass & vocals
Jimmy Edmonds, fiddles & piano
